solution_code: public class Solution {--newline--    public List<Integer> inorderTraversal(TreeNode root) {--newline--        List<Integer> list = new ArrayList<Integer>();--newline--    --newline--        Stack<TreeNode> stack = new Stack<TreeNode>();--newline--        TreeNode cur = root;--newline--    --newline--        while(cur!=null || !stack.empty()){--newline--            while(cur!=null){--newline--                stack.add(cur);--newline--                cur = cur.left;--newline--            }--newline--            cur = stack.pop();--newline--            list.add(cur.val);--newline--            cur = cur.right;--newline--        }--newline--    --newline--        return list;--newline--    }--newline--}
